profile:
A locally owned full service painting company based on Vancouver Island and serving Nanaimo to Comox Valley & Campbell River. Providing painting and decorating services for Residential, Commercial, Interior and Exterior. Specializing in Residential repaints as well as Custom/High End homes and Commercial projects too. Fully insured and licensed.

Superior expertise in painting, staining & wallpaper. Certified Journeymen Red Seal Painter/Decorator with 10 years experience in the trade to help with all your painting/decorating needs!
